            <title>[BATCH-262] Hibernate Job  blocks on flush</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/BATCH-262</link>
                <project id="10090" key="BATCH">Spring Batch</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hibernate Job  blocks on flush (using real database).  The driving query input source is putting a range lock on the Customer objects.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
